strings: <voice_0x01001C96><se_high>Princess Medea: You know, this forest reminds me of something.
<voice_0x01001C97><se_high>Princess Medea: Remember that time we snuck out of the castle?
<voice_0x01001C98><se_high>Princess Medea: I begged and pleaded with you to take me to Farebury. Finally you gave in and smuggled me out of the castle in disguise! Remember?
<voice_0x01001C99><se_high>Princess Medea: You thought of everything, even packed lunches! But then we got lost in the woods, and it started to get dark.

<voice_0x01001C9A><se_high>Princess Medea: I remember being so scared.
I was crying. When suddenly, Munchie jumped out of your pocket and took off like a shot!
<voice_0x01001C9B><se_high>Princess Medea: By the time we caught up with him, we'd somehow ended up back at the castle gates!
<voice_0x01001C9C><se_high>Princess Medea: Munchie really is a very special mouse...
